title: authme问题
author: 唯爱她°
txt_content:
[AuthMe] Downloading GEO IP database, because the old database is older than 30 days or doesn't exist
[17:08:16] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 6/WARN]: [AuthMe] No MaxMind credentials found in the configuration file! GeoIp protections will be disabled.
[17:08:16] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 6/INFO]: [AuthMe] There is no newer GEO IP database uploaded to MaxMind. Using the old one for now.
[17:08:16] [Server thread/INFO]: [Citizens] Loaded 0 NPCs.
[17:08:16] [Craft Scheduler Thread - 6/WARN]: [AuthMe] Could not download GeoLiteAPI database [FileNotFoundException]: plugins\AuthMe\GeoLite2-Country.mmdb (系统找不到指定的文件。)复制代码看后台有这个信息[AuthMe] Could not download GeoLiteAPI database [FileNotFoundException]: plugins\AuthMe\GeoLite2-Country.mmdb (系统找不到指定的文件。)特别是这一段，是啥意思啊啊，，我去搜GeoLiteAPI这个变量并没有搜到。顺便请大佬看下我另外几个帖子。。。。
